(2, '02', 'Bachelor of Information Technology', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width: 500px;\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				Gelar:</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; line-height: 16.866666793823242px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Bachelor of Information Technology</span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				SKS :</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				110</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				Joint Degree:</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 11pt; line-height: 16.866666793823242px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Fontys University and Saxion University</span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong>DESCRIPTION</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	The bachelor of Information Technology (BIT) class is a credit Transfer programme between institute Sains Terapan dan Teknologi Surabaya (iSTTS) and overseas universities: Swinburne University of Technology and Murdoch University focusing on Infromation Technology. Students who finish this course will earn an IT degree:</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	&bull; Bachelor of Information Technology from Swinburne University of Technology</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	&bull; Bachelor of Science in Cyber Forensic an Information Security and Computer Science, Murdoch University Australian (Singapore Campus)</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	<strong>STUDY DURATION</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	Having completed the first 4 (four) semesters of the study at ISTTS, student will be able to diversify their educational experience by spending the last 3 (three semesters) at Swinburne University of Technology, Melbourne-Australia, or at Murdoch University Australia, Singapore Campus by spending 1.5 (one and a half) years.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	<strong>CAMPUS PROFILE</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	Swinburne University of Technology<br />\r\n	Founded in 1908, Swinburne is a well-known university in Australia with strong business and industry focus. It has the highest graduate full-time employment rate in Victoria, 3rd in Australia. It is a government funded university.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	Murdoch University<br />\r\n	As one of Australia&rsquo;s leading university, Murdoch University is a progressive, dynamic and modern institution with an International reputation for quality teaching excellence research and satisfaction. Murdoch University is ranked in the world&rsquo;s Top 100 Universities under 50 years old. (Times Higher Education 2016- Top 150 global universities under 50 years old) and offers over 80 degrees as well as post graduate degree programmes.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	In this course, you&rsquo;ll learn how to identify and respond to threats and information security incidents for government agencies and corporate organisations. You&rsquo;ll learn how to forensically examine digital evidence and develop strong analytical and critical thinking skills with a focus on computer crime investigation. As part of your studies, you&rsquo;ll completed practical experience and have the opportunity to engage who are currently making significant contributions to information technology research and who have a strong passion for teaching.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	STUDY FOCUS</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	Swinburne University of Technology<br />\r\n	- Net enterprise<br />\r\n	- Java and J2EE Enterprise<br />\r\n	- Software Engineering</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	Murdoch University<br />\r\n	- Cyber Forensic<br />\r\n	- Information Security<br />\r\n	- Business Intelligence</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	<strong>JOINT DEGREE PROGRAMME</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n	DESCRIPTION</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n	The Joint Degree Program enables student to get two prestigious degrees from iSTTS and the partner university from Netherlands, Fontys University of Applied Sciences and Saxion University of Applied Sciences. Graduates form the Joint Degree may pursue a career at international companies at the Netherlands.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n	STUDY DURATION</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n	Having completed the first 6 (six) semesters of the study at iSTTS, student is offered a Joint Degree options to finish his/her study for 2 (two) last semester at :</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n	1. Fontys University of Applied Sciences, Eindhoven, the Netherlands, for<br />\r\n	- Teknik Elektro: Sarjana Teknik and Bachelor of Electronic Engineering<br />\r\n	- Teknik Informatika: Sarjana Komputer and Bachelor of Information and Communication&nbsp; Technology<br />\r\n	- Sistem Informasi Bisnis: Sarjana Sistem Informasi and Bachelor of Business Information System</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n	2. Saxion University of Applied Sciences, Deventer the Netherlands, for<br />\r\n	- Teknik Industri: Sarjana Teknik and Bachelor Business Engineering<br />\r\n	- Desain Komunikasi Visual: Sarjana Desain and Bachelor Art and Technology<br />\r\n	- Desain&nbsp; Produk: Sarjana Desain dan Bachelor of Art and Technology</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	<strong>CAMPUS PROFILE</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	Fontys University of Applied Sciences and Sciences<br />\r\n	The name &lsquo;Fontys&rsquo; is derived from the Latin word &lsquo;Fons&rsquo; which means &lsquo;source&rsquo;. Fontys Aspires to be a dynamic source of knowledge, development, innovation and inspiration. It is a well-known name in education, not only in the Netherlands, but also in many other parts of the world. Fontys is the second largest institute for higher education in the Netherlands.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	Saxion University of Applied Sciences<br />\r\n	One of the largest institutions of higher education in the Netherlands, with over 24,000 students (and still growing!). Saxion University has a rich history &ndash; its roots can be traced back to the 1875. A merger of two educational institutions, the Hogeschool Enschede and&nbsp; Hogeschool Ijselland, in 1998 paved the way for Saxion University in its present form. This merger enabled Saxion to build further on its strong position in Dutch higher educational and since education and since then Saxion University has come to be rocognised as an important center of expertise at regional, national and international level.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	<strong>CREDIT TRANSFER PROGRAMME</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	REQUIREMENTS<br />\r\n	Entry requirement include a GPA of 2.5 during the first two years at STTS and IELTS score of band 6.0</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	LIVING COST<br />\r\n	Per year, it will cost around AUD 15.000 &ndash; AUD 20.000 at Melbourne or SGD 16.800 &ndash; SGD 18.000 at Singapore.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	REMARKS<br />\r\n	Students who take this programme will save a lot of money (about 50% or more) in less time while earning prestigious Bachelor Degree.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	<strong>JOINT DEGREE PROGRAMME</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	REQUIREMENTS<br />\r\n	Entry requirements include a GPA of 3.0 during the first three years at iSTTS and TOEFL score of 550 (or IELTS score of band 6.0)</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	LIVING COST<br />\r\n	Living cost per year is approximately EUR 7.000</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	REMARKS<br />\r\n	During the one-year at Fontys or Saxion, student must undertake an industry internship for one semester. They may get some allowance of EUR 300 &ndash; 400 per month. There are also scholarships available for top students.</p>\r\n', ' 	  <table style=\"width: 500px;\" cellspacing=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" border=\"1\"> 	<tbody> 		<tr> 			<td><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 				Degree:</font></font></td> 			<td> 				<span style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0