(3, '10', 'Strata-1 Teknik Elektro', '<table class=\"table table-bordered\" style=\"float:right; margin-left:20px; margin-top:10px; width:300px\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">TAHUN BERDIRI</span></td>\r\n			<td style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">1979</span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">AKREDITASI</span></td>\r\n			<td style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">B</span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">GELAR</span></td>\r\n			<td style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Sarjana Teknik (S. T.)</span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">MASA STUDI</span></td>\r\n			<td style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">8 Semester, 144 SKS</span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Deskripsi</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\">Elektro adalah program studi yang yang mempelajari rangkaian elektronika yang dipakai dalam kehidupan sehari hari sampai dengan Industri.<br />\r\n	Mahasiswa akan mempelajari ilmu dasar elektronika sampai teknologi yang terbaru dengan tujuan agar lulusan mampu menggunakan, memodifikasi, hingga membuat teknologi baru.<br />\r\n	Revolusi Industri 4.0 yang menekankan penggunaan komputer dan di ikuti Revolusi Industri 4.0 yang menggunakan teknologi Jaringan dan Internet dalam sistem komunikasi digital merupakan bagian penting di dalam bidang elektro saat ini.<br />\r\n	Ketrampilan praktis untuk berkarya pada dunia kerja serta menciptakan lapangan kerja sebagai technopreneur merupakan bagian yang juga penting untuk diberikan kepada mahasiswa.</font></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Visi</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Program studi S1 Teknik Elektro iSTTS mampu menghasilkan sumber daya manusia yang menguasai teknologi Elektronika dan Komputer agar berperan dalam peningkatan mutu kehidupan di tingkat Nasional maupun Internasional.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Misi</span></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"list-style-type:circle\">\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Menyelenggarakan kegiatan akademis yang efektif dan relevan dengan kebutuhan masyarakat dan industri.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Mendorong penyelenggaraan kegiatan penelitian dalam bidang elektronika dan komputer yang tepat guna.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Membangun kerja sama dengan kelompok masyarakat dan dunia industri untuk mendapat kesempatan mengabdikan ilmu dan teknologi.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Fokus Pendidikan</span></span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"list-style-type:circle\">\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>Industrial Automation</strong></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px; text-align:justify\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Bidang Industrial Automation mempelajari sistem pengendalian dan pengawasan mesin-mesin dalam sebuah pabrik dengan peralatan elektronik sehingga dapat bekerja secara otomatis. Peralatan elektronik yang pada umumnya dipergunakan disebut Programmable Logic Controller (PLC) yang juga dapat dihubungkan dengan software aplikasi terintegrasi antara Human Machine Interface (HMI) dan Supervisory Control and Data Acquisition (SCADA). Bidang ini mempersiapkan lulusan dalam menangani berbagai masalah pengendalian mesin dalam pabrik dengan konsep terintegrasi.</span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"list-style-type:circle\">\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>Internet of Things</strong></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px; text-align:justify\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Dunia internet di masa depan akan menjadi wadah penampung seluruh informasi. Informasi pada internet dapat dimanfaatkan untuk membuat peralatan / mesin menjadi otomatis, cerdas, dapat dikendalikan jarak jauh, dan dilakukan antara mesin dan mesin, ataupun mesin dan smartphone, dan semuanya menggunakan jalur komunikasi internet. Bidang ini mempersiapkan agar lulusan dapat menangani pengendalian berbagai peralatan/mesin melalui jaringan internet yang semakin mudah dan murah.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"list-style-type:circle\">\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>Renewable Power System</strong></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px; text-align:justify\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Energi terbarukan adalah energi yang berasal dari proses alam yang berkelanjutan seperti tenaga surya, angin, arus air, proses biologi, ataupun panas bumi. Energi terbarukan merupakan alternatif yang terus dikembangkan guna menjaga ketersediaan energi dan daya listrik. Bidang ini mempersiapkan agar lulusan dapat menangani pemanfaatan daya listrik terbarukan dengan dibantu penerapan distribusi tenaga listrik supaya energi terbarukan bisa tersalur dan terkendali secara efisien.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px\">keistimewaan jurusan</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	1. Kurikulum yang up to date dan tanggap atas tantangan indusri digital dan elektronika</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	2. Menekankan pada Computer Based Education, agar mahasiswa juga dapat menguasai teknologi &nbsp; &nbsp;terkini</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	3. Kegiatan perkuliahan yang didukung oleh praktikum di laboratorium yang dilengkapi dengan teknologi terbaru</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	4. Kunjungan ke berbagai perusahaan untuk melihat lapangan dan kebutuhan market</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	5. Praktek kerja di perusahaan wajib dilakukan oleh mahasiswa, agar dapat mengimplementasikan ilmu yang didapat selama kuliah</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	6. Memiliki inkubator untuk mendukung start up bisnis dibidang elektronika digital dan energi terbarukan.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	7. Bimbingan dan pendanaan diluar jam kuliah. Mahasiswa diberikan kesempatan untuk mengerjakan project diluar jam kuliah. Kegiatan ini bertujuan agar mahasiswa dapat menggunakan ilmu yang telah dipelajari dan mendapatkan pengalaman.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Prospek Karir</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Lulusan Teknik Elektro iSTTS banyak bekerja di berbagai perusahaan swasta maupun pemerintah baik dalam perancangan, dan pengembangan peralatan produksi, termasuk sebagai :</span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"list-style-type:circle\">\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n		Perancang Peralatan Elektronik</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n		Perancang Sistem Kendali Mesin-mesin Industri</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n		Perancang Jaringan Komputer</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n		Perancang Aplikasi IoT (Internet of Things)</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n		Pengendali Pembangkit Listrik dengan Energi Terbarukan</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<table class=\"table table-bordered\" style=\"float:right; margin-left:20px; margin-top:10px; width:300px\"> 	<tbody> 		<tr> 			<td style=\"text-align:justify\"> 				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">SINCE</font></font></span></td> 			<td style=\"text-align:justify\"> 				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">1979</font></font></span></td> 		</tr> 		<tr> 			<td style=\"text-align:justify\"> 				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">ACCREDITATION</font></font></span></td> 			<td style=\"text-align:justify\"> 				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">B</font></font></span></td> 		</tr> 		<tr> 			<td style=\"text-align:justify\"> 				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">DEGREE</font></font></span></td> 			<td style=\"text-align:justify\"> 				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Bachelor of Engineering (ST)</font></font></span></td> 		</tr> 		<tr> 			<td style=\"text-align:justify\"> 				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">STUDY PERIOD</font></font></span></td> 			<td style=\"text-align:justify\"> 				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">8 Semesters, 144 credits</font></font></span></td> 		</tr> 	</tbody> </table> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Description</font></font></span></span></p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	<font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Electrical is a study program that studies electronic circuits used in everyday life up to the industry. </font></font><br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	Students will study basic electronics until the latest technology with  the aim that graduates are able to use, modify, and create new  technologies. </font></font><br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	The Industrial Revolution 4.0 which emphasized the use of computers and  followed the Industrial Revolution 4.0 that used Network technology and  the Internet in digital communication systems is an important part in  the current electro field. </font></font><br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	Practical skills to work in the world of work and create jobs as technopreneur is an important part to give to students.</font></font></font></p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Vision</font></font></span></span></p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">S1  Electrical Engineering study program iSTTS is able to produce human  resources who master Electronic and Computer technology to play a role  in improving the quality of life at the National and International  level.</font></font></span></p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	<span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Mission</font></font></span></span></p> <ul style=\"list-style-type:circle\"> 	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"> 		<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Organizing academic activities that are effective and relevant to the needs of society and industry.</font></font></span></li> 	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"> 		<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Encouraging the implementation of research activities in the field of electronics and computers that are appropriate.</font></font></span></li> 	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"> 		<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Building cooperation with community groups and the industrial world to get the opportunity to devote science and technology.</font></font></span></li> </ul> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	<span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Education Focus</font></font></span></span></p> <ul style=\"list-style-type:circle\"> 	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"> 		<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Industrial Automation</font></font></strong></span></li> </ul> <p style=\"margin-left:40px; text-align:justify\"> 	<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">The  Industrial Automation field studies the control and supervision of  machines in a factory with electronic equipment so that it can work  automatically. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Electronic  equipment that is generally used is called a Programmable Logic  Controller (PLC) which can also be connected with integrated application  software between Human Machine Interface (HMI) and Supervisory Control  and Data Acquisition (SCADA). </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">This field prepares graduates to deal with various machine control problems in a factory with an integrated concept.</font></font></span></p> <ul style=\"list-style-type:circle\"> 	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"> 		<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">The Internet of Things</font></font></strong></span></li> </ul> <p style=\"margin-left:40px; text-align:justify\"> 	<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">The world of internet in the future will become a container for all information. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Information  on the internet can be used to make equipment / machines automated,  intelligent, can be controlled remotely, and carried out between  machines and machines, or machines and smartphones, and all of them use  internet communication lines. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">This  field prepares graduates to be able to handle a variety of equipment /  machinery through an internet network that is increasingly easy and  inexpensive.&nbsp;</font></font></span></p> <ul style=\"list-style-type:circle\"> 	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"> 		<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Renewable Power System</font></font></strong></span></li> </ul> <p style=\"margin-left:40px; text-align:justify\"> 	<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Renewable  energy is energy that comes from sustainable natural processes such as  solar, wind, water currents, biological processes, or geothermal energy.  </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Renewable energy is an  alternative that is constantly being developed in order to maintain the  availability of energy and electricity. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">This  field prepares graduates to be able to handle the utilization of  renewable electricity with the help of the application of electricity  distribution so that renewable energy can be distributed and controlled  efficiently.</font></font></span></p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	<span style=\"font-size:18px\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">majors majors</font></font></span></p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	1. An up-to-date and responsive curriculum for the challenges of the digital and electronic industries</font></font></p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	2. Emphasis on Computer Based Education, so students can also master the latest technology</font></font></p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	3. Lecture activities supported by practicum in laboratories equipped with the latest technology</font></font></p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	4. Visits to various companies to see the field and market needs</font></font></p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	5. Work practices in companies must be carried out by students, in  order to be able to implement the knowledge gained during college</font></font></p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	6. Have an incubator to support start-up businesses in the field of digital electronics and renewable energy.</font></font></p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	7. Guidance and funding outside of class hours. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Students are given the opportunity to work on projects outside of class hours. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">This activity aims to enable students to use the knowledge they have learned and gain experience.</font></font></p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	<span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Career Prospects</font></font></span></span></p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">ISTTS  Electrical Engineering graduates work in various private and government  companies both in the design and development of production equipment,  including as:</font></font></span></p> <ul style=\"list-style-type:circle\"> 	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 		Electronic Equipment Designer</font></font></li> 	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 		Designers of Industrial Machinery Control Systems</font></font></li> 	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 		Computer Network Designer</font></font></li> 	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 		IoT (Internet of Things) Application Designer</font></font></li> 	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 		Renewable Energy Generators</font></font></li> </ul> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	&nbsp;</p>', 1);
INSERT INTO `jurusan_bahasa` (`jurusan_bahasa_id`, `jurusan_id`, `jurusan_nama`, `jurusan_deskripsi_1`, `jurusan_deskripsi_2`, `bahasa_id`) VALUES
(4, '11', 'Strata-1 Informatika', '<table class=\"table table-bordered\" style=\"float:right; margin-left:20px; margin-top:10px; width:300px\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">TAHUN BERDIRI</span></td>\r\n			<td style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">1985</span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">AKREDITASI</span></td>\r\n			<td style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">B</span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">GELAR</span></td>\r\n			<td style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Sarjana Komputer (S.Kom)</span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">MASA STUDI</span></td>\r\n			<td style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">8 Semester, 144 SKS</span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Deskripsi</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	Informatika merupakan bidang yang &nbsp; menghubungkan antara manusia denganinformasi&nbsp;melalui pengembangan sistem, servis, teknologi, dan interface.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	Bidang ini mempelajari bagaimana teknologi informasi mengubah pola hidup manusia. Mahasiswa akan belajar memanfaatkan komputasi untuk problem solving menggunakan teknologi informasi yang sangat dinamis dan terus berkembang.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	Cakupan bidang informatika meliputi: algoritma, pemrograman, perancangan dan analisis sistem, arsitektur komputer, jaringan komputer, kecerdasan buatan, sistem cerdas, rekayasa perangkat lunak, pengembangan web, pengembangan mobile app, service based system.Mahasiswa dapat memilih satu dari tiga fokus yaitu: Computational Intelligence, Software Technology, dan Internet Technology.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Visi</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Pada Tahun 2027, menjadi program studi Informatika yang berkualitas, inovatif, dan unggul di tingkat nasional serta mampu bersaing di tingkat Asia Tenggara dengan tetap mengedepankan nilai-nilai ke Indonesiaan.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Misi</span></span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n		Memberikan materi pendidikan dan pengajaran terbaik di bidang Informatika sehingga menghasilkan lulusan yang tangguh dan terampil sesuai dengan kebutuhan dunia kerja.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Melakukan penelitian yang kreatif dan inofatif di bidang Informatika, sesuai kebutuhan masyarakat dan perkembangan teknologi.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Menjalin kerjasama dengan berbagai lembaga dan menyediakan solusi kreatif untuk masalah-masalah bidang Informatika di Indonesia.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\">Fokus Pendidikan</span></span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>Computer Science</strong></span><br />\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Computer Science merupakan bidang ilmu yang memeberikan kontribusi terbesar dalam perkembangan Information and Communication Technology (ICT) yang begitu pesat saat ini. Menyelesaikan permasalahan kompleks dengan memanfaatkan sejumlah algoritma yang efektif merupakan salah satu elemen yang menjadi fokus kuliah. Fokus lainnya adalah membangun sistem komputer cerdas dalam menyelesaikan berbagai permasalahan secara otomatis, tanpa bantuan manusia.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>Internet Technology</strong></span><br />\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Jaringan web yang semakin luas menuntut penelitian dalam bidang internet. Sebagai salah satu fokus dalam Teknik Informatika, bidang ini mengajarkan pengembangan aplikasi mobile di berbagai platform seperti Android dan iOS. Selain itu, bidang ini juga mengajarkan pemanfaatan teknologi internet untuk mengembangkan bisnis di dunia internet, sekaligus merancang dan mengembangkan jaringan komputer untuk perusahaan kecil sampai perusahaan berskala enterprise.</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>Software Engineering</strong></span><br />\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Konsentrasi Software Technology membekali mahasiswa dengan kemampuan teknikal yang mendalam dalam bidang pemrograman untuk berbagai platform perangkat lunak dengan menggunakan tools, teknologi dan framework terkini, memimpin tim pengembang perangkat lunak atau bekerja sama dengan anggota lain dalam tim, merekayasa perangkat lunak berskala besar dan kompleks, serta merancang perangkat lunak yang berorientasi pada user. Mahasiswa akan menguasai Pemahaman yang mendalam tentang struktur dan arsitektur perangkat lunak dan juga skill secara mendalam untuk mengembangkan sistem berbasis komputer yang baru,&nbsp; serta memelihara aplikasi yang sudah ada sesuai dengan kebutuhan dari organisasi.&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px; text-align:justify\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Keistimewaan Jurusan</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong>&#9679; &nbsp;Prodi dengan Mata Kuliah AI terlengkap</strong><br />\r\n	S1-Informatika memiliki daftar mata kuliah berbasis kecerdasan buatan terlengkap. Pada matakuliah wajib terdapat 2 mata kuliah dasar AI: Basic AI dan Soft Computing sedangkan pada Mata kuliah pilihan terdapat mata kuliah yang lebih applied seperti Advance Machine Learning, Computer Vision, Web Mining, Data Mining, Natural Language Processing, Big Data Processing dan lain-lain.</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>&#9679; Kurikulum yang Up-to-date</strong><br />\r\n	Materi perkuliahan dan praktikum yang diajarkan di Teknik Informatika tidak akan pernah<br />\r\n	ketinggalan zaman, karena secara rutin diperbarui sesuai dengan kebutuhan pasar. Dosen-dosen iSTTS juga terus mengembangkan ilmu dengan studi lanjut. Dalam 2018-2019 saja ada 5 Doktor baru pada jajaran pengajar di prodi&nbsp; S1-Informatika iSTTS baik dari Luar negeri maupun dari dalam negeri.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>&#9679; Karir Mapan di Perusahaan Skala Enterprise</strong><br />\r\n	Berdiri sejak 1985, Strata 1 Informatika iSTTS telah meluluskan lebih dari 4200 alumni yang telah bekerja, baik di dalam maupun di luar negeri. Beberapa perusahaan dengan nama besar seperti BCA, Sampoerna, dan Djarum Group secara rutin melakukan rekrutmen terhadap alumni S1-Informatika iSTTS. Beberapa alumni berprestasi bahkan berhasil mendapatkan pekerjaan di Google, Electronic Art, Opera, dan Facebook. Alumni yang tidak ingin bekerja di perusahaan, kebanyakan telah menjadi technopreneur dalam bidang teknologi informasi. </span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>&#9679; Karir menantang di perusahaan Unicorn</strong><br />\r\n	Pada beberapa tahun terakhir alumni S1 Informatika iSTTS juga diminati para unicorn seperti Traveloka, Tokopedia dan Bukalapak.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong>&#9679; Kerjasama dan peluang Beasiswa</strong><br />\r\n	Informatika iSTTS telah bekerjasama dengan beberapa Universitas di luar negeri untuk meningkatkan kualitas pendidikan seperti dengan Swinburne University of technology, Melbourne-Australia. Murdoch University, Perth-Australia. Fontys University of App Science, Netherland. NCTU- Taiwan. NTUST-Taiwan. Kerjasama ini juga memberikan kesempatan bagi mhs S1 Informatika untuk studi lanjut S2 di Luar negeri dan mendapatkan peluang beasiswa.</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Prospek Karir</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Lulusan Strata-1 Teknik Informatika dan Komputer memiliki prospek karir di bidang Teknologi Informasi khususnya teknik pengembangan perangkat lunak, beberapa jenis karir yang umum dipilih misalnya :</span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"list-style-type:circle\">\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Software Developer</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">System Administrator</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Network Administrator</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">IT Researcher</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">System Analyst</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Technopreneur</span></li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Project Manager</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<table class=\"table table-bordered\" style=\"float:right; margin-left:20px; margin-top:10px; width:300px\"> 	<tbody> 		<tr> 			<td style=\"text-align:justify\"> 				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">SINCE</font></font></span></td> 			<td style=\"text-align:justify\"> 				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">1985</font></font></span></td> 		</tr> 		<tr> 			<td style=\"text-align:justify\"> 				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">ACCREDITATION</font></font></span></td> 			<td style=\"text-align:justify\"> 				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">B</font></font></span></td> 		</tr> 		<tr> 			<td style=\"text-align:justify\"> 				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">DEGREE</font></font></span></td> 			<td style=\"text-align:justify\"> 				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Bachelor of Computer (S.Kom)</font></font></span></td> 		</tr> 		<tr> 			<td style=\"text-align:justify\"> 				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">STUDY PERIOD</font></font></span></td> 			<td style=\"text-align:justify\"> 				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">8 Semesters, 144 credits</font></font></span></td> 		</tr> 	</tbody> </table> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	<span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Description</font></font></span></span></p> <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	Informatics is a field that connects humans with information through  the development of systems, services, technology, and interfaces.</font></font></p> <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	This field studies how information technology changes the pattern of human life. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Students will learn to use computing for problem solving using information technology that is very dynamic and growing.</font></font></p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	The scope of the informatics field includes: algorithms, programming,  system design and analysis, computer architecture, computer networks,  artificial intelligence, intelligent systems, software engineering, web  development, mobile app development, service based systems. Students can  choose one of three focuses, namely: Computational Intelligence,  Software Technology, and Internet Technology.</font></font></p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	<span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Vision</font></font></span></span></p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">In  2027, it will become a high-quality, innovative and superior  Informatics study program at the national level and be able to compete  at the Southeast Asian level while continuing to promote values ??to  Indonesia.</font></font></span></p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	<span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Mission</font></font></span></span></p> <ul> 	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 		Providing the best education and teaching material in the field of  Informatics so as to produce graduates who are tough and skilled  according to the needs of the workforce.</font></font></li> 	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"> 		<span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Conducting  creative and innovative research in the field of Informatics, according  to community needs and technological development.</font></font></span></li> 	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"> 		<span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Establish  cooperation with various institutions and provide creative solutions to  problems in the field of Informatics in Indonesia.</font></font></span></li> </ul> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Education Focus</font></font></span></span></p> <ul> 	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"> 		<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Computer Science</font></font></strong></span><br> 		<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">  Computer Science is the field of science that has made the biggest  contribution in the rapid development of Information and Communication  Technology (ICT) today. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Solving complex problems by utilizing a number of effective algorithms is one of the elements that is the focus of the lecture. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Another focus is on building intelligent computer systems in solving various problems automatically, without human assistance.</font></font></span></li> 	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"> 		<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Internet Technology</font></font></strong></span><br> 		<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> An increasingly widespread web network demands research in the field of the internet. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">As  one of the focuses in Informatics Engineering, this field teaches the  development of mobile applications on various platforms such as Android  and iOS. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">In addition, this  field also teaches the use of internet technology to develop business  in the internet world, as well as designing and developing computer  networks for small companies to enterprise-scale companies.</font></font></span></li> 	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"> 		<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Software Engineering</font></font></strong></span><br> 		<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">  The concentration of Software Technology equips students with deep  technical skills in the field of programming for various software  platforms by using the latest tools, technology and frameworks, leading  software development teams or working with other members in a team,  engineering large-scale and complex software , as well as designing  user-oriented software. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Students  will master a deep understanding of the structure and architecture of  software as well as in-depth skills to develop new computer-based  systems, and maintain existing applications according to the needs of  the organization.&nbsp;</font></font></span></li> </ul> <p style=\"margin-left:40px; text-align:justify\"> 	&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	<span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Department Privileges</font></font></span></span></p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	<span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<br> 	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">? Complete AI Study Program with</font></font></strong><br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">  	S1-Informatics courses has the </font><strong><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">most complete</font></strong><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> list of artificial intelligence-based courses. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">In  compulsory courses there are 2 basic AI courses: Basic AI and Soft  Computing while in elective courses there are more applied courses such  as Advanced Machine Learning, Computer Vision, Web Mining, Data Mining,  Natural Language Processing, Big Data Processing and others- other.</font></font></span></span></span></p> <p> 	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">? Up-to-date curriculum Course</font></font></strong><br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">  	material and practicum taught in Informatics will never be </font></font><br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	out of date, because it is regularly updated according to market needs. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">ISTTS lecturers also continue to develop knowledge with further study. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">In  2018-2019 there were only 5 new Doctors in the teaching ranks of iSTTS  S1-Informatics study programs both from abroad and from within the  country.</font></font></span></span></p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">? Well-established Career in Enterprise Scale Company</font></font></strong><br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">  	Founded in 1985, the Strata 1 Informatics iSTTS has graduated more than 4200 alumni who have worked both at home and abroad. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Some big name companies such as BCA, Sampoerna, and Djarum Group routinely recruit recruitment of S1-Informatics alumni iSTTS. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Some outstanding alumni even managed to get jobs at Google, Electronic Art, Opera, and Facebook. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Alumni who do not want to work in companies, most have become technopreneur in the field of information technology.</font></font></span></span></p> <p> 	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">? Challenging careers at Unicorn companies</font></font></strong><br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">   	In recent years S1 iSTTS alumni of Informatics are also in demand by  unicorns such as Traveloka, Tokopedia and  Bukalapak.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  </font></font></span></span></p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><strong><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">? Cooperation and opportunities</font></font></strong><br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">  	iSTTS Information </font><strong><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Scholarships</font></strong><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">  have collaborated with several universities abroad to improve the  quality of education such as Swinburne University of technology,  Melbourne-Australia. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Murdoch University, Perth-Australia. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Fontys University of App Science, Netherland. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">NCTU- Taiwan. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">NTUST-Taiwan. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">This  collaboration also provides an opportunity for undergraduate students  of Informatics to study further Masters abroad and get scholarship  opportunities.</font></font></span></span></p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	<span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Career Prospects</font></font></span></span></p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Strata-1  graduates of Information and Computer Engineering have career prospects  in the field of Information Technology especially software development  techniques, several types of careers are commonly chosen for example:</font></font></span></p> <ul style=\"list-style-type:circle\"> 	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"> 		<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Software Developer</font></font></span></li> 	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"> 		<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">System Administrator</font></font></span></li> 	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"> 		<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Network Administrator</font></font></span></li> 	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"> 		<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">IT Researcher</font></font></span></li> 	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"> 		<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">System Analyst</font></font></span></li> 	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"> 		<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Technopreneur</font></font></span></li> 	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"> 		<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Project Manager</font></font></span></li> </ul> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	&nbsp;</p>', 1),
(5, '12', 'Strata-1 Teknik Industri', '<table class=\"table table-bordered\" style=\"float:right; margin-left:20px; margin-top:10px; width:300px\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n				TAHUN BERDIRI</td>\r\n			<td style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n				1992</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n				AKREDITASI</td>\r\n			<td style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n				B</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n				GELAR</td>\r\n			<td style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n				Sarjana Teknik (S.T.)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n				MASA STUDI</td>\r\n			<td style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n				8 Semester, 144 SKS</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px\">Deskripsi</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	Di era modern, Teknik Industri menjadi salah satu ilmu teknik yang memegang peranan terpenting dalam pengelolaan berbagai sistem industri, baik industri manufaktur/ barang maupun jasa. Teknik Industri (Industrial Engineering) adalah ilmu teknik yang mencakup bidang perencanaan, desain, instalasi, perbaikan, dan pengembangan sistem terintegrasi yang terdiri dari sumber daya manusia, material, energi, peralatan, dan informasi. Di iSTTS, setiap sarjana Teknik Industri dipersiapkan sebagai industrial system designer, industrial problem analyzer, industrial problem solver, dan &nbsp;technopreneur yang handal memanfaatkan teknologi terkini dalam menghadapi dinamika bisnis global.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px\">Visi</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	Pada Tahun 2022, program Studi Teknik Industri menjadi program studi teknik bidang ilmu teknik industri yang beretika, berkualitas, inovatif, berwawasan &nbsp;lingkungan, dan cepat tanggap terhadap masalah masyarakat lokal maupun Indonesia dengan mengedepankan sistem tata kelola organisasi yang efisien.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px\">Misi</span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"list-style-type:circle\">\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		Memberikan materi pendidikan dan pengajaran terbaik di bidang teknik industri yang terbaik, dalam sistem tata kelola organisasi yang efisien, disesuaikan dengan situasi dan kondisi kebutuhan masyarakat Indonesia.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		Bekerja sama dengan berbagai program studi terkait dan pelaku industri di Indonesia, melakukan penelitian terapan bidang ilmu, teknologi, dan desain industri yang disesuaikan dengan situasi, kondisi, dan kebutuhan masyarakat Indonesia dalam rangka peningkatan daya saing ekonomi.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		Menyediakan berbagai solusi inovatif dan unggulan berbasis ilmu, teknologi, dan desain industri bagi berbagai masalah masyarakat Indonesia khususnya dalam menghadapi pasar masyarakat ekonomi ASEAN (MEA).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px\">Fokus Pendidikan</span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"list-style-type:circle\">\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		<strong>Manufacturing system</strong><br />\r\n		Pembelajaran difokuskan pada hal-hal yang berhubungan dengan perancangan berbagai jenis sistem dan sub-sistem operasional dalam industri manufaktur, misalnya Computer Aided Manufacturing, Sustainable Manufacturing, industrial automation, maintenance &nbsp;management, dan lain-lain.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		<strong>Quality Management</strong><br />\r\n		Dalam konsentrasi ini, pembelajaran difokuskan pada hal-hal yang berhubungan dengan perancangan hingga pelaksanaan manajemen kualitas di berbagai jenis industri, contohnya: analisis keputusan dan resiko, standarisasi industri (ISO, HACCP, SNI, dll), performance management, dsb.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px\">Keistimewaan Jurusan</span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"list-style-type:circle\">\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		<strong>Pembelajaran yang sangat bersahabat</strong><br />\r\n		&ldquo;Kampus adalah rumah kedua,&rdquo; demikian pendekatan yang dilakukan dalam proses pembelajaran dan hubungan sosial di jurusan Teknik Industri iSTTS. Keakraban dan keramahan hubungan dosen-mahasiswa, maupun antar mahasiswa dipercaya sebagai kunci keberhasilan transfer pengetahuan dan keahlian ilmu teknik industri, bahkan diterapkan sejak awal masa orientasi yang kreatif, gembira, dan bebas dari segala bentuk perploncoan.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		<strong>Pembekalan Ilmu &amp; Teknologi Industri Manufaktur Terkini</strong><br />\r\n		Sejak 2016, Teknik Industri menjadi salah satu education partner PLM Siemens-Plano US di dunia dan satu-satunya program jurusan Teknik Industri di Indonesia yang mendapat dukungan penuh dalam hal penggunaan perangkat lunak product life-cycle management tercanggih di dunia. Artinya, setiap mahasiswa Teknik Industri akan dibekali kemampuan/ keahlian berbasis teknologi terkini yang bersifat global.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		<strong>Pengayaan Ilmu Manajemen Lingkungan Industrial Modern</strong><br />\r\n		Sejak 2006, Teknik Industri iSTTS menjadi satu dari dua jurusan Teknik Industri se-Indonesia yang dipercaya oleh ASEAN Society for Environmental Protection sebagai penyelenggara pembelajaran Environmental Management Accounting (EMA). Dengan menguasai sub-bidang ilmu manajemen lingkungan industrial ini, setiap lulusan Teknik Industri diharapkan memiliki kompetensi yang relevan dengan berbagai isu lingkungan industrial.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		<strong>Pembelajaran Lapangan secara Intensif</strong><br />\r\n		Hubungan yang dekat antara jurusan Teknik Industri iSTTS dengan pelaku usaha berbagai sektor industri di banyak daerah di Indonesia, khususnya Jawa Timur, menjadi kelebihan lain dari Jurusan Teknik Industri iSTTS. Proses penajaman kemampuan dan wawasan industrial dilakukan lewat mata kuliah Kerja Praktek dan kunjungan rutin/ semester ke berbagai perusahaan manufaktur dan jasa.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px\">prospek karir</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	Lulusan Strata-1 Teknik Industri memiliki beberapa jenis karir yang umum dipilih misalnya :</p>\r\n<ul style=\"list-style-type:circle\">\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		Ergonomic Engineer</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		Plant Manager</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		Industrial Product Designer</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		Quality Control Manajer</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		TQM, Kaizen Implementator</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		CAD/ CAM Engineer</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		Product Planner &amp; Inventory Controller</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		Commercial Distribution Analyst &amp; Engineer.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		Enviromental Managerial Accounting (EMA) Developer.</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		Customer Relation Management (CRM) Officer</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		Occupational Safety, Health, Enviromental (SHE)&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		&nbsp;engineer/ officer</li>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n		Marketer</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<table class=\"table table-bordered\" 