eering that covers the fields of planning, design,  installation, repair and development of integrated systems consisting of  human, material, energy, equipment, and information resources. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">At  iSTTS, every Bachelor of Industrial Engineering is prepared as an  industrial system designer, industrial problem analyzer, industrial  problem solver, and technopreneur who is capable of utilizing the latest  technology in dealing with the dynamics of global business.</font></font></p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	<span style=\"font-size:18px\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Vision</font></font></span></p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	In 2022, the Industrial Engineering Study Program will become an  engineering study program in the field of industrial engineering that is  ethical, quality, innovative, environmentally sound, and responsive to  the problems of local and Indonesian communities by promoting an  efficient organizational governance system.</font></font></p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	<span style=\"font-size:18px\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Mission</font></font></span></p> <ul style=\"list-style-type:circle\"> 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 		Providing the best educational and teaching materials in the best  industrial engineering, in an efficient organizational governance  system, adapted to the situations and conditions of the needs of the  Indonesian people.</font></font></li> 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 		Collaborating with various related study programs and industry players  in Indonesia, conducting applied research in the fields of science,  technology and industrial design that is adapted to the situation,  conditions and needs of the Indonesian people in the context of  increasing economic competitiveness.</font></font></li> 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 		Providing various innovative and excellent solutions based on science,  technology and industrial design for various problems of the Indonesian  people, especially in dealing with the ASEAN economic community (MEA)  market.</font></font></li> </ul> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	<span style=\"font-size:18px\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Education Focus</font></font></span></p> <ul style=\"list-style-type:circle\"> 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"> 		<strong><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Manufacturing system</font></font></strong><br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">   		Learning is focused on matters relating to the design of various types  of operational systems and sub-systems in the manufacturing industry,  such as Computer Aided Manufacturing, Sustainable Manufacturing,  industrial automation, maintenance management, and others.</font></font></li> 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"> 		<strong><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Quality Management</font></font></strong><br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">   		In this concentration, learning is focused on matters relating to  design to the implementation of quality management in various types of  industries, for example: decision and risk analysis, industry  standardization (ISO, HACCP, SNI, etc.), performance management, etc.</font></font></li> </ul> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	<span style=\"font-size:18px\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Department Privileges</font></font></span></p> <ul style=\"list-style-type:circle\"> 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"> 		<strong><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Very friendly learning</font></font></strong><br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">   		\"Campus is a second home,\" according to the approach taken in the  learning process and social relations in the Department of Industrial  Engineering iSTTS. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Familiarity  and friendliness of the lecturer-student relationship, as well as  between students, is believed to be the key to the success of the  transfer of knowledge and expertise in industrial engineering, even  being applied since the beginning of a creative, happy, and free from  all forms of hazing.</font></font></li> 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"> 		<strong><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Provision of the Latest Manufacturing Industry Science &amp; Technology</font></font></strong><br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">   		Since 2016, Industrial Engineering has become one of the Siemens-Plano  US PLM education partners in the world and the only Industrial  Engineering program in Indonesia that has full support in the use of the  most sophisticated product life-cycle management software in world. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">That is, every Industrial Engineering student will be equipped with the latest global technology-based capabilities / expertise.</font></font></li> 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"> 		<strong><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Enrichment of Modern Industrial Environmental Management Science</font></font></strong><br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">   		Since 2006, iSTTS Industrial Engineering has become one of two majors  in Industrial Engineering in Indonesia that is trusted by the ASEAN  Society for Environmental Protection as the organizer of learning  Environmental Management Accounting (EMA). </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">By  mastering this industrial environmental management sub-field, each  Industrial Engineering graduate is expected to have competencies  relevant to various industrial environmental issues.</font></font></li> 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"> 		<strong><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Intensive Field Learning</font></font></strong><br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">   		The close relationship between the Department of Industrial  Engineering iSTTS with businesses of various industrial sectors in many  regions in Indonesia, especially East Java, is another advantage of the  Department of Industrial Engineering iSTTS. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">The  process of sharpening industrial capability and insight is carried out  through Job Training courses and regular / semester visits to various  manufacturing and service companies.&nbsp;</font></font></li> </ul> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	<span style=\"font-size:18px\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">career prospects</font></font></span></p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	Strata-1 Industrial Engineering graduates have several commonly chosen careers for example:</font></font></p> <ul style=\"list-style-type:circle\"> 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 		Ergonomic Engineer</font></font></li> 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 		Plant Manager</font></font></li> 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 		Industrial Product Designer</font></font></li> 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 		Quality Control Manager</font></font></li> 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 		TQM, Kaizen Implementer</font></font></li> 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 		CAD / CAM Engineer</font></font></li> 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 		Product Planner &amp; Inventory Controller</font></font></li> 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 		Commercial Distribution Analyst &amp; Engineer.</font></font></li> 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 		Environmental Managerial Accounting (EMA) Developer.</font></font></li> 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 		Customer Relationship Management (CRM) Officer</font></font></li> 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 		Occupational Safety, Health, Environmental (SHE)&nbsp;</font></font></li> 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 		&nbsp;engineer / officer</font></font></li> 	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 		Marketer</font></font></li> </ul> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	&nbsp;</p>', 1);
