(6, '14', 'Desain Produk', '<table class=\"table table-bordered\" style=\"float:right; margin-left:20px; margin-top:10px; width:315px\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">TAHUN BERDIRI</span></td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">2010</span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">AKREDITASI</span></td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">B</span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">GELAR</span></td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Sarjana Desain (S.Ds.)</span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">MASA STUDI</span></td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">8 Semester, 144 SKS</span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>\r\n				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Joint Degree</span></td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Saxion University of Applied Sciences</span></td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Deskripsi</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">S1 - Desain Produk iSTTS adalah Program Studi yang memadukan desain dan teknologi otomasi untuk menghasilkan produk yang tidak hanya menarik secara tampilan, tetapi memiliki fungsi smart product .&nbsp;<br />\r\n	Hal ini membuat Desain Produk iSTTS menjadi sangat unik dan sejalan dengan pergerakan Industri 4.0. Kemampuan Desain ditambah dengan pemahaman teknologi otomasi akan memberikan nilai plus bagi mahasiswa Desain Produk iSTTS. Sehingga mahasiswa siap menjawab tantangan Industri 4.0 di Indonesia maupun mancanegara.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Visi</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Melahirkan sumber daya manusia yang terdepan dalam penguasaan Teknologi bidang Desain Produk yang mampu bersaing di tingkat Asia Tenggara dan mengedepankan kualitas, inovasi serta nilai-nilai keindonesiaan. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Misi</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Menyelenggarakan pendidikan di bidang Desain Produk Industri yang menekankan pada penguasaan Teknologi Modern dan Desain untuk pengembangan kreativitas desain dan inovasi produk dengan beberapa warna keindonesiaan di dalamnya, mengacu pada berbagai standar internasional, disesuaikan dengan situasi dan kondisi kebutuhan dan perkembangan sosial, ekonomi, dan budaya masyarakat Asia Tenggara. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Fokus Pendidikan :</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 40px;\">\r\n	&#9679; Desain Produk Cerdas (Smart Product Design) :</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 40px;\">\r\n	mahasiswa difokuskan pada desain produk dengan memanfatkan sensor, arduino, wireless, dll dengan tujuan supaya mereka mampu menciptakan produk cerdas yang inovatif sehingga mampu menyelesaikan masalah dalam kehidupan manusia sehari-hari. Baik produk yang diproduksi secara masif atau produk dengan spesifikasi khusus dalam jumlah terbatas.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n	&#9679; Desain Kriya Modern :</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">\r\n	mahasiswa difokuskan pada pengembangan ide dan konsep styling untuk perhiasan, sepatu, produk apparel selain sepatu, mainan, miniatur, dan ekplorasi pemanfaatan material.<br />\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n	&#9679; Desain Transportasi :</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">\r\n	mahasiswa difokuskan pada pengembangan ide serta konsep styling untuk exterior maupun interior sarana transportasi. Seperti mobil, kereta api, sepeda, kendaraan niaga, serta kendaraan pada taman-taman hiburan (Theme Parks).<br />\r\n	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n	&#9679; Desain Interior :</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">\r\n	mahasiswa difokuskan pada pengembangan ide serta konsep styling berbagai macam produk interior yang mencakup furniture, lampu, pencahayaan ruang, serta produk-produk dekoratif interior lainnya.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Keistimewaan Program Studi</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 40px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">1. Program studi yang menggabungkan Desain dan Teknologi Otomasi untuk menghasilkan Smart Product.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 40px;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">2. Melatih mahasiswa untuk berempati dengan lingkungan sekitar untuk menciptakan dan mengembangkan sebuah produk.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 40px;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">3. Mengadakan kuliah tamu bagi mahasiswa, dengan menghadirkan mentor/pembicara dengan keahlian khusus, untuk &nbsp;menambah wawasan dan kreativitas mahasiswa.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 40px;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">4. Praktik kerja di perusahaan wajib dilakukan sebelum masuk dunia kerja.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 40px;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">5. Mahasiswa dilatih mengerjakan proyek dalam tim, agar dapat membangun kerjasama, melatih kreativitas dan tanggung jawab.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 40px;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">6. Kunjungan ke perusahaan untuk menambah wawasan mahasiswa rutin dilakukan setiap semester.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 40px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><strong>Kompetensi Lulusan S1 Desain Produk iSTTS:</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 40px;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n	1. Mampu melakukan sketsa tangan dengan baik dan benar.<br />\r\n	2. Memahami teknologi dan proses manufaktur produk secara teori dan praktik.<br />\r\n	3. Menguasai aplikasi komputer 2D, 3D dan animasi.<br />\r\n	4. Menguasai pembuatan Prototype Produk secara manual maupun digital.<br />\r\n	5. Mampu berpikir ilmiah, kreatif, dan inovatif dalam menyelesaikan permasalahan dengan desain.<br />\r\n	6. Mampu menyajikan konsep inovatif secara visual dengan baik dan benar.<br />\r\n	7. Mampu melakukan Programming untuk kebutuhan Smart Product.<br />\r\n	8. Memiliki kemampuan manajerial dalam pengembangan bisnis dibidang desain produk.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 40px;\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 40px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">Prospek karir untuk lulusan S1 Desain Produk iSTTS adalah:</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 40px;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\">1. Smart Product Designer<br />\r\n	2. Toys Designer<br />\r\n	3. Footware Designer<br />\r\n	4. Fashion Accessories Designer<br />\r\n	5. Transportation Designer<br />\r\n	6. Interior Designer<br />\r\n	7. Enterpreneur<br />\r\n	8. R&amp;D</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<table class=\"table table-bordered\" style=\"float:right; margin-left:20px; margin-top:10px; width:315px\"> 	<tbody> 		<tr> 			<td> 				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">SINCE</font></font></span></td> 			<td> 				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">2010</font></font></span></td> 		</tr> 		<tr> 			<td> 				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">ACCREDITATION</font></font></span></td> 			<td> 				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">B</font></font></span></td> 		</tr> 		<tr> 			<td> 				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">DEGREE</font></font></span></td> 			<td> 				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Bachelor of Design (S.Ds.)</font></font></span></td> 		</tr> 		<tr> 			<td> 				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">STUDY PERIOD</font></font></span></td> 			<td> 				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">8 Semesters, 144 credits</font></font></span></td> 		</tr> 		<tr> 			<td> 				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Joint Degree</font></font></span></td> 			<td> 				<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Saxion University of Applied Sciences</font></font></span></td> 		</tr> 	</tbody> </table> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	<span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Description</font></font></span></span></p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">S1  - iSTTS Product Design is a Study Program that combines design and  automation technology to produce products that are not only attractive  in appearance, but have a smart product function.&nbsp;</font></font><br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	This makes iSTTS Product Design very unique and in line with Industry 4.0 movement. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Design  skills coupled with an understanding of automation technology will  provide added value for iSTTS Product Design students. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">So students are ready to answer the challenges of Industry 4.0 in Indonesia and abroad.&nbsp;</font></font></span></p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	<span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Vision</font></font></span></span></p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Give  birth to leading human resources in the mastery of Technology in the  field of Product Design that is able to compete at the Southeast Asian  level and prioritizes quality, innovation and Indonesian values. &nbsp;  &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</font></font></span></p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	<span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Mission</font></font></span></span></p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Organizing  education in the field of Industrial Product Design that emphasizes the  mastery of Modern Technology and Design for the development of creative  designs and product innovations with several Indonesian colors in it,  referring to various international standards, adapted to the situations  and conditions of needs and social, economic, and cultural development  of the community Southeast Asia. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</font></font></span></p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	<span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Education Focus:</font></font></span></span></p> <p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 40px;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	? Smart Product Design:</font></font></p> <p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 40px;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	students are focused on product design by utilizing sensors, arduino,  wireless, etc. with the aim that they are able to create innovative  intelligent products so as to solve problems in everyday human life. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Either a mass-produced product or a product with special specifications in limited quantities.</font></font></p> <p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"> 	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	? Modern Craft Design:</font></font></p> <p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	students are focused on developing styling ideas and concepts for  jewelry, shoes, apparel products in addition to shoes, toys, miniatures,  and exploration of material use. </font></font><br> 	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	? Transportation Design:</font></font></p> <p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	students are focused on developing ideas and styling concepts for exterior and interior transportation facilities. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Such as cars, trains, bicycles, commercial vehicles, and vehicles in theme parks. </font></font><br> 	&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	? Interior Design:</font></font></p> <p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	students are focused on developing ideas and styling concepts for a  variety of interior products including furniture, lamps, room lighting,  and other interior decorative products.</font></font></p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	&nbsp;</p> <ul> </ul> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	<span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Privileges of Study Programs</font></font></span></span></p> <p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 40px;\"> 	<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">1. Study programs that combine Design and Automation Technology to produce Smart Products.</font></font></span></p> <p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 40px;\"> 	<br> 	<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">2. Train students to empathize with the surrounding environment to create and develop a product.</font></font></span></p> <p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 40px;\"> 	<br> 	<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">3.  Conduct guest lectures for students, by presenting mentors / speakers  with special expertise, to add insight and creativity to students.</font></font></span></p> <p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 40px;\"> 	<br> 	<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">4. Work practices in companies must be done before entering the workforce.</font></font></span></p> <p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 40px;\"> 	<br> 	<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">5. Students are trained to work on projects in teams, so they can build cooperation, practice creativity and responsibility.</font></font></span></p> <p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 40px;\"> 	<br> 	<span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">6. Visits to companies to broaden students\' insights are routinely conducted every semester.</font></font></span></p> <p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 40px;\"> 	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><strong><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Competencies of Graduates of iSTTS Product Design S1:</font></font></strong></span></p> <p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 40px;\"> 	<br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	1. Able to do hand sketches properly and correctly. </font></font><br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	2. Understand the technology and product manufacturing processes in theory and practice. </font></font><br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	3. Mastering 2D, 3D and animation computer applications. </font></font><br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	4. Mastering the manufacture of Product Prototype manually or digitally. </font></font><br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	5. Able to think scientifically, creatively, and innovatively in solving problems with design. </font></font><br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	6. Able to present innovative concepts visually well and correctly. </font></font><br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	7. Able to do Programming for Smart Product needs. </font></font><br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	8. Has managerial skills in business development in the field of product design.</font></font></p> <p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 40px;\"> 	&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 40px;\"> 	<span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Career prospects for graduates of iSTTS Product Design S1 are:</font></font></span></span></p> <p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 40px;\"> 	<br> 	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">1. Smart Product Designer </font></font><br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	2. Toys Designer </font></font><br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	3. Footware Designer </font></font><br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	4. Fashion Accessories Designer </font></font><br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	5. Transportation Designer </font></font><br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	6. Interior Designer </font></font><br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	7. Entrepreneur </font></font><br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	8. R&amp;D</font></font></span></span></p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	&nbsp;</p>', 1),
(7, '17', 'Desain Komunikasi Visual', '<table class=\"table table-bordered\" style=\"width:390px; float:right; margin-left: 20px; margin-top: 17px;\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td class=\"s gr\">\r\n				TAHUN BERDIRI</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				2008</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td class=\"s gr\">\r\n				AKREDITASI</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				B<br />\r\n				SK No. 164/SK/BAN-PTAk-VI/S/VIII/2013</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td class=\"s gr\">\r\n				GELAR</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				Sarjana Desain (S.Ds.)</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td class=\"s gr\">\r\n				MASA STUDI</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n				8 Semester, 144 SKS</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p class=\"l dgr title\">\r\n	Deskripsi<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;: &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	Desain Komunikasi Visual (DKV) iSTTS berfokus pada 3 pilar utama yaitu Seni, Teknologi, dan Bisnis. Kurikulum Program Studi selalu mengakomodasi kebutuhan dunia desain visual yang selalu berkembang, sehingga lulusan DKV STTS mampu bersaing dalam pasar global khususnya dunia industri kreatif.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n	Seni<br />\r\n	Mahasiswa DKV iSTTS akan belajar teori dan berlatih ketrampilan seni rupa dan desain agar memiliki dasar yang kuat dalam berkarya. Mereka juga akan dilatih untuk memacu kreatifitas, memiliki kepekaan estetika dan mampu mengapresiasi karya seni.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Teknologi<br />\r\n	Dengan latar belakangnya yang kuat di bidang teknologi, tidak perlu diragukan lagi kemampuan DKV iSTTS dalam melatih mahasiswa agar mampu menggunakan teknologi multimedia semaksimal mungkin untuk meningkatkan produktivitasnya dalam berkarya. Yang perlu diingat, teknologi tidak bisa menciptakan kreativitas, namun teknologi sangat membantu dalam meningkatkannya.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	Bisnis<br />\r\n	Ide cemerlang bisa hilang, bila tak terealisasikan menjadi karya. Karya yang bagus tak akan jadi nyata tanpa dukungan sumberdaya. Namun bila ketrampilan manajemen dimiliki, maka ketrampilan ini bisa meningkatkan kualitas sarana/prasarana bagi perkembangan kreatifitas dan kemunculan karya-karya selanjutnya. Mahasiswa DKV iSTTS akan dilatih dalam hal ini, sehingga mereka punya kemampuan untuk menjalankan bisnis desain dan berwirausaha.</p>\r\n<p class=\"l dgr title\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"l dgr title\" style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">\r\n	<strong>Visi</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">\r\n	Program Studi Desain Komunikasi Visual iSTTS menjadi program studi unggulan di bidang DKV berbasis teknologi komputer yang mampu bersaing di tingkat Asia Tenggara, dengan mengedepankan kualitas, inovasi dan nilai-nilaikeindonesiaan.</p>\r\n<p class=\"m gr\" style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">\r\n	<strong>Misi</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"m gr\" style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">\r\n	Menyelenggarakan pendidikan yang berorientasi pada bidang desain komunikasi visual yang berbasis teknologi komputer, menggiatkan penelitian yang memberikan kontribusi pada perkembangan dunia desain dan menerapkan keilmuan dan ketrampilan dalam pengembangan industri kreatif di masyarakat, sesuai dengan Tridarma Perguruan Tinggi (Pendidikan, Penelitian dan Pengabdian pada Masyarakat).</p>\r\n<p class=\"l dgr title\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"l dgr title\">\r\n	<strong>Tujuan</strong></p>\r\n<ul class=\"gr ss m\" type=\"circle\">\r\n	<li class=\"sp\">\r\n		Mampu mengapresiasi seni terapan, memiliki ketrampilan dan keahlian dalam karya yang nyata yang dibutuhkan oleh masyarakat dan dunia industri.</li>\r\n	<li class=\"sp\">\r\n		Mampu memanfaatkan teknologi komputer untuk meningkatkan produktvitas dalam berkarya.</li>\r\n	<li class=\"sp\">\r\n		Mampu berkompetensi dalam dunia kerja dan mampu menciptakan industri kreatif yang mennyerap tenaga kerja.</li>\r\n	<li class=\"sp\">\r\n		Mampu meneliti dan menciptakan inovasi baru di bidang seni terapan.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"l dgr title\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"l dgr title\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong>Fokus pendidikan</strong></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Menjelang semester akhir mahasiswa DKV STTS akan memilih bidang peminatan sesuai minat mereka masing-masing. Pemilihan dilakukan dengan mengambil setidaknya tiga mata kuliah pilihan (MKP). Bidang peminatan yang tersedia adalah:</p>\r\n<p class=\"l dgr title\">\r\n	Animasi<br />\r\n	Bagi mahasiswa yang tertarik pada 3D modeling dan pembuatan animasi 3D, maka bidang peminatan ini akan mengajarkan ketrampilan berdasar teknologi terbaru untuk membekali mereka terjun ke dunia yang sedang hot saat ini. Matakuliah yang bisa dipilih adalah: 3D Modeling, Special Effects dan Motion Graphics.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Sinematography/Perfilman<br />\r\n	Dengan memilih mata kuliah bagi bidang ini, yaitu: Sinematografi, Advertising Film, dan Film Experimental, maka mahasiswa yang tertarik untuk berkarya dalam media film bisa lebih siap untuk menghasilkan karya film yang mampu bersaing dalam mutu.</p>\r\n<p class=\"l dgr title\">\r\n	Ilustrasi dan Komik<br />\r\n	Industri komik adalah industri kreatif yang menarik minat banyak anak muda. Bagi mahasiswa yang berminat dan memiliki bakat dan ketrampilan dalam menggambar ilustrasi, pastilah bidang peminatan ini menjadi pilihan mereka. Di dalamnya mereka akan medapatkan kuliah: Graphic Novel, Characters Design dan Advanced Digital Drawing.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Fotografi<br />\r\n	Bila media foto menjadi pilihan, maka mahasiswa DKV bisa memantapkan ilmu mereka pada bidang ini sekaligus belajar bagaimana membuat karya mereka agar bisa &#39;dijual&#39; dan &#39;menjual&#39;, serta menuntun mereka untuk menjadi fotografer yang profesional. Mata kuliah yang ditawarkan adalah: Fotografi Desain, Fotografi Eksperimental dan Fotografi Bisnis.<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"l dgr title\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"l dgr title\">\r\n	<strong>Fasilitas</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"m gr\">\r\n	Sebagai program studi yang bergerak dalam bidang seni terapan, tentu saja kegiatan perkuliahan tidak hanya dilakukan di kelas. Kegiatan perkuliahan yang berupa praktik langsung akan menyertai banyak mata kuliah di DKV iSTTS. Praktik yang menggunakan media tradisional dilakukan di studio, sedang praktik yang menggunakan media digital dilakukan dalam laboratorium.</p>\r\n<p class=\"m gr\">\r\n	Dalam studio mahasiswa bisa mengerjakan materi dan tugas yang diberikan saat perkuliahan. DKV iSTTS memberikan sesi praktik ini tanpa perlu biaya lagi. Misalnya terdapat matakuliah sebanyak 3 SKS, maka mahasiswa mendapat pertemuan kelas selama 3 SKS dan mendapat pertemuan studio selama 2 SKS tanpa biaya tambahan.</p>\r\n<p class=\"m gr\">\r\n	DKV iSTTS mengutamakan kemampuan mahasiswa dalam menguasai media digital. Untuk mencapai hal itu maka diberikan fasilitas berupa laboratorium yang dilengkapi dengan teknologi terkini. Tersedia komputer yang dilengkapi dengan tablet Wacom berukuran A4 yang bisa digunakan mahasiswa untuk membuat digital illustration atau digital sculpting. DKV iSTTS juga telah bekerjasama dengan banyak software provider sehingga semua program yang digunakan adalah software original yang legal.</p>\r\n<p class=\"m gr\">\r\n	Selain fasilitas tersebut terdapat juga terdapat fasilitas untuk bidang fotografi dan perfilman. Tersedia kamera-kamera SLR, kamera video, lighting set bahkan green screen studio yang bisa digunakan mahasiswa untuk membuat karya-karya audio-visual dan sinematografi.</p>\r\n<p class=\"m gr\">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"m gr\" style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">\r\n	<strong>Sarjana Desain Komunikasi Visual (DKV) iSTTS dapat berprofesi di bidang:</strong></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-left: 40px;\">\r\n	<li class=\"m gr\">\r\n		Designer grafis</li>\r\n	<li class=\"m gr\">\r\n		Periklanan</li>\r\n	<li class=\"m gr\">\r\n		Percetakan</li>\r\n	<li class=\"m gr\">\r\n		Ilustrasi dan Komik</li>\r\n	<li class=\"m gr\">\r\n		Film Production</li>\r\n	<li class=\"m gr\">\r\n		Animasi</li>\r\n	<li class=\"m gr\">\r\n		Profesi lainnya yang membutuhkan kreativitas dan keterampilan di bidang desain dan multimedia &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<table class=\"table table-bordered\" style=\"width:390px; float:right; margin-left: 20px; margin-top: 17px;\"> 	<tbody> 		<tr> 			<td class=\"s gr\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 				SINCE</font></font></td> 			<td><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 				2008</font></font></td> 		</tr> 		<tr> 			<td class=\"s gr\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 				ACCREDITATION</font></font></td> 			<td><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 				B </font></font><br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 				SK No. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">164 / SK / BAN-PTAk-VI / S / VIII / 2013</font></font></td> 		</tr> 		<tr> 			<td class=\"s gr\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 				DEGREE</font></font></td> 			<td><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 				Bachelor of Design (S.Ds.)</font></font></td> 		</tr> 		<tr> 			<td class=\"s gr\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 				STUDY PERIOD</font></font></td> 			<td><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 				8 Semesters, 144 credits</font></font></td> 		</tr> 	</tbody> </table> <p class=\"l dgr title\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	Description </font></font><span style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">&nbsp;:  &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</font></font></span></p> <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	Visual Communication Design (DKV) iSTTS focuses on 3 main pillars namely Art, Technology, and Business. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">The  Study Program curriculum always accommodates the needs of the  ever-evolving visual design world, so that DKV STTS graduates are able  to compete in the global market, especially the creative industries.</font></font></p> <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"> 	<br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	Arts </font></font><br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	DKV iSTTS students will study theory and practice fine arts and design skills so they have a strong foundation in their work. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">They will also be trained to stimulate creativity, have aesthetic sensitivity and be able to appreciate works of art.</font></font></p> <p><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	Technology </font></font><br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	With a strong background in technology, there is no doubt that the  ability of DKV iSTTS in training students to be able to use multimedia  technology as much as possible to increase their productivity in the  work. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">The thing to remember, technology can not create creativity, but technology is very helpful in improving it.</font></font></p> <p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	Business </font></font><br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	Ideas can be lost brilliantly, if not realized into works. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Good work will not be possible without the support of resources. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">However,  if management skills are possessed, these skills can improve the  quality of facilities / infrastructure for the development of creativity  and the appearance of subsequent works. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">DKV iSTTS students will be trained in this matter, so they have the ability to run a design and entrepreneurial business.</font></font></p> <p class=\"l dgr title\"> 	&nbsp;</p> <p class=\"l dgr title\" style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"> 	<strong><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Vision</font></font></strong></p> <p style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	ISTTS Visual Communication Design Study Program has become a leading  study program in the field of computer technology-based DKV that is able  to compete at the Southeast Asian level, by promoting quality,  innovation and Indonesian-values.</font></font></p> <p class=\"m gr\" style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"> 	<strong><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Mission</font></font></strong></p> <p class=\"m gr\" style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	Organizing education oriented in the field of visual communication  design based on computer technology, intensifying research that  contributes to the development of the design world and applying science  and skills in the development of creative industries in society, in  accordance with the Tridarma of Higher Education (Education, Research  and Community Service).</font></font></p> <p class=\"l dgr title\"> 	&nbsp;</p> <p class=\"l dgr title\"> 	<strong><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Aim</font></font></strong></p> <ul class=\"gr ss m\" type=\"circle\"> 	<li class=\"sp\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 		Able to appreciate applied arts, have the skills and expertise in real work needed by the community and the industrial world.</font></font></li> 	<li class=\"sp\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 		Able to use computer technology to improve productivity in the work.</font></font></li> 	<li class=\"sp\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 		Able to be competent in the world of work and be able to create creative industries that absorb labor.</font></font></li> 	<li class=\"sp\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 		Able to research and create new innovations in the field of applied arts.</font></font></li> </ul> <p class=\"l dgr title\"> 	&nbsp;</p> <p class=\"l dgr title\"> 	<span style=\"font-size:12px;\"><strong><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Education focus</font></font></strong></span></p> <p><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	Towards the final semester DKV STTS students will choose the specialization field according to their respective interests. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">The selection is made by taking at least three elective courses (MKP). </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">The specialization fields available are:</font></font></p> <p class=\"l dgr title\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	Animation </font></font><br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	For students who are interested in 3D modeling and making 3D animation,  this specialization field will teach the skills based on the latest  technology to equip them to dive into a hot world today. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Subjects to choose from are: 3D Modeling, Special Effects and Motion Graphics.</font></font></p> <p><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	Cinematography / Film </font></font><br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	By selecting courses for this field, namely: Cinematography,  Advertising Film, and Experimental Film, students interested in working  in film media can be better prepared to produce film work that is able  to compete in quality.</font></font></p> <p class=\"l dgr title\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	Illustration and Comics </font></font><br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	The comic industry is a creative industry that attracts many young people. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">For  students who are interested and have the talent and skills in drawing  illustrations, this specialization course will be their choice. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">In it they will get lectures: Graphic Novel, Characters Design and Advanced Digital Drawing.</font></font></p> <p><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	Photography </font></font><br><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	If photo media becomes the choice, DKV students can solidify their  knowledge in this field while learning how to make their work so that it  can be \'sold\' and \'sold\', and guides them to become professional  photographers. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">The courses offered are: Design Photography, Experimental Photography and Business Photography.</font></font><br> 	&nbsp;</p> <p class=\"l dgr title\"> 	&nbsp;</p> <p class=\"l dgr title\"> 	<strong><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Amenities</font></font></strong></p> <p class=\"m gr\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	As a study program engaged in the field of applied arts, of course lecturing activities are not only carried out in class. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Lecture activities in the form of direct practice will accompany many courses at DKV iSTTS. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Practices  that use traditional media are done in the studio, while practices that  use digital media are carried out in laboratories.</font></font></p> <p class=\"m gr\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	In the studio students can work on the material and assignments given during lectures. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">DKV iSTTS provides this practice session at no additional cost. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">For  example there are as many as 3 SKS courses, then students get class  meetings for 3 SKS and get studio meetings for 2 SKS without additional  fees.</font></font></p> <p class=\"m gr\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	DKV iSTTS prioritizes students\' ability in mastering digital media. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">To achieve this, facilities are provided in the form of laboratories equipped with the latest technology. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">A computer equipped with an A4 Wacom tablet can be used by students to make digital illustration or digital sculpting. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">DKV iSTTS has also collaborated with many software providers so that all programs used are original legal software.</font></font></p> <p class=\"m gr\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	In addition to these facilities there are also facilities for the field of photography and film. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Available  SLR cameras, video cameras, lighting sets and even green screen studios  that can be used by students to create audio-visual and cinematographic  works.</font></font></p> <p class=\"m gr\"> 	&nbsp;</p> <p class=\"m gr\" style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"> 	<strong><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Bachelor of Visual Communication Design (DKV) iSTTS can work in the fields of:</font></font></strong></p> <ul style=\"margin-left: 40px;\"> 	<li class=\"m gr\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 		Graphic Designer</font></font></li> 	<li class=\"m gr\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 		Advertising</font></font></li> 	<li class=\"m gr\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 		Printing</font></font></li> 	<li class=\"m gr\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 		Illustration and Comic</font></font></li> 	<li class=\"m gr\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 		Film Production</font></font></li> 	<li class=\"m gr\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 		Animation</font></font></li> 	<li class=\"m gr\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 		Other professions that require creativity and skills in the field of  design and multimedia &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</font></font></li> </ul>', 1);
