></font></strong> 		<p><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 			Students are given the knowledge and insight on the latest  Information Technology accompanied by use and utilization in the world  of work</font></font></p> 	</li> </ul> <ul style=\"list-style-type:circle\"> 	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"> 		<strong><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">USEFUL IN THE INDUSTRIAL &amp; BUSINESS ENVIRONMENT</font></font></strong></li> </ul> <p style=\"margin-left:40px; text-align:justify\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	Utilization of Information Technology to help decision making in the Industrial and Business environment. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Research  is carried out starting in the second semester, followed by scientific  publications and thesis writing to contribute to society. </font><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">The choice of research direction is Science and the use of Information Technology.</font></font></p> <ul style=\"list-style-type:circle\"> 	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"> 		<strong><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">OLD STUDY</font></font></strong> 		<ul> 			<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 				Contains 42 credits taken in 4 semesters with a composition:</font></font></li> 			<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 				6 Mandatory MK x 3 SKS = 18 SKS</font></font></li> 			<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 				4 Elective MK x 3 credits = 12 credits</font></font></li> 			<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 				12 SKS Research and Thesis</font></font></li> 		</ul> 	</li> 	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"> 		<strong><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">AMENITIES</font></font></strong></li> </ul> <p style=\"margin-left:40px; text-align:justify\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	There is a comfortable lecture room equipped with a computer, wifi,  lecture material, coffee break and dinner as well as teachers who are  competent in their fields.</font></font></p> <p style=\"margin-left:40px; text-align:justify\"> 	&nbsp;</p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	<span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\">Career Prospects</font></font></span></span></p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 	Information Technology Masters graduates have career prospects in the field of information technology, including:</font></font></p> <p style=\"text-align:justify\"> 	&nbsp;</p> <ul> 	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 		Practitioners in various disciplines who have insight into information technology</font></font></li> 	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 		Consultant in the field of Information Technology</font></font></li> 	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 		Professionals in Information Technology</font></font></li> 	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"><font style=\"vertical-align: inherit;\"> 		IT Lecturer, Educator.</font></font></li> </ul>', 1);
